      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REGAL GYPSY (1) promising dog unbeaten so far from four runs. Comes into this on the back of a slick 21.59) win at Q Lakeside. Three of her wins have been this trip. Can continue winning ways. CYCLONE TIM (7) continues to race in super honest form hitting the frame at five of 11 career runs, winning two back before finishing third last time (19.15) over 350m at this track. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. Rates a winning chance on best. MAJESTIC ETHICS (6) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (19.48) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. EXTRA SHARP (8) is new here but is not to be underestimated.",
